{"tid":1985892,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"名帥肥賓亂世來港教波 兩名瑞典國腳抵港訓練","createTime":"2020-04-23T12:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T10:27:38.000Z","uid":9030,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"a06ddec4c2d05b9d3909dd4a590751595dbf240e","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:51:46.000Z","msg":"現為中超球隊大連人主教練的賓尼迪斯目前在港，消息指他近日不時在跑馬地指導兩名球員訓練，據悉為瑞典國腳森拿臣及馬古斯丹尼爾臣。<br />\n<br />\n受到武漢肺炎影響，康文署關閉所有足球場，但跑馬地遊樂場內每日仍有不少人活動，包括使用足球場，有人發現曾帶領利物浦的領隊、現為中超球隊大連人主教練的賓尼迪斯，近日不時在跑馬地遊樂場的足球場上教波，惟球員只有兩人，未有違反限聚令。據悉，該兩名球員為剛加盟大連人的瑞典國腳森拿臣及馬古斯丹尼爾臣，兩人正於香港辦理簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200423/large/1587636385_4791.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200423%2Flarge%2F1587636385_4791.jpg&h=ecf350a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed95e51706f74e9439145f99a8a92693ef862c3e","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:54:01.000Z","msg":"消息指賓尼迪斯已來港超過20日"},{"pid":"0b60c4b44c5f7e48486a033fc66ff0d2d4d305ee","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/ZZYslX4R8cyT0FbraO/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FZZYslX4R8cyT0FbraO%2Fgiphy.gif&h=7f625aae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a8228c3ea8e0b6d94c94bcfb1508d7d57300d92","tid":1985892,"uid":201464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:58:27.000Z","msg":"嚟香港練波做乜？"},{"pid":"645f9e4d2e0022b94586b79d11b466eca4448014","tid":1985892,"uid":166474,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"6a8228c3ea8e0b6d94c94bcfb1508d7d57300d92","tid":1985892,"uid":201464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:58:27.000Z","msg":"嚟香港練波做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"避開支那瘟疫"},{