 src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日不少香港利物浦球迷聞風分批到跑馬地球場，希望「捕獲」這位前紅軍名帥時，可是賓尼迪斯今日未有帶兩名瑞典新兵現身跑馬地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"佢應該知俾人點左相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9373d48fd556ca2bb1da52db8f4c8e3573a7fbd6","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:07:59.000Z","msg":"賓尼迪斯再現跑馬地 簽名合照冇托手踭"},{"pid":"b02a53e6380a0c8cd3cc9b975f89b34ba50532c3","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"身在香港的中超球隊大連人主教練賓尼迪斯昨日在中環閒逛購物後，今午與兩名瑞典國腳森拿臣及馬古斯丹尼爾臣在跑馬地球場操練，他收操表示，暫未知何時可以返回中國領軍。"},{"pid":"9adaa31718d5ed5131a1c16a14bb83ade9a0eb5d","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:09:40.000Z","msg":"每位2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8BEA6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8BEA6a.png&h=292128a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abb89c6869bf6f8cfc9c22035592e0d57a0fde16","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:10:26.000Z","msg":"賓帥今日甫到場，前冠忠南區中場溫俊主動與對方閒談，約50分鐘訓練時，多次被球迷或在場內做運動的人士要求合照，難得他有求必應，不介意被打斷訓練。完成訓練後，再有數名球迷帶備波衫、海報及賓帥自傳等要求他簽名，當然還有合照，他全部冇托手踭，還與球迷閒談。"},{"pid":"b7afc94af18cf9c2185acd6c07850257b4715218","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"笑死, 嚇走人<br />\n<br />\n有球迷問賓帥明日會否再到這裏操練，賓帥回覆指未必到場"},{"pid":"425ea497004c3ced58ce3af9cf959b7bff55d9e5","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n操練後，記者嘗試問賓帥會否受訪，他禮貌地表示，今次在港想低調點，故不會回答，還要求記者不要拍照，而他謂，暫時未必知何時離開香港返回中國，可能是明天，可能是數天後，要視乎情況。"},{"pid":"ef1ca119931674e17392a4197cf1ab0ad5beb494","tid":1985892,"uid":136226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abb89c6869bf6f8cfc9c22035592e0d57a0fde16","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:10:26.000Z","msg":"賓帥今日甫到場，前冠忠南區中場溫俊主動與對方閒談，約50分鐘訓練時，多次被球迷或在場內做運動的人士要求合照，難得他有求必應，不介意被打斷訓練。完成訓練後，再有數名球迷帶備波衫、海報及賓帥自傳等要求他簽名，當然還有合照，他全部冇托手踭，還與球迷閒談。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0521237319a820e4c0809c28d3650a139ca862c","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"溫俊: I am hk footballer, sign me to Dalian pls<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYnMf7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYnMf7b.png&h=948ba70e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e69f3bc38929fc082cbc6ad10c38165a0367f64b","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"還要求記者不要拍照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200425/large/1587801358_74ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200425%2Flarge%2F1587801358_74ca.jpg&h=e2a65ee2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7153e678ab2191ac606a35788147d6a45dcdf648","tid":1985892,"uid":9030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:17:37.000Z","msg":"溫俊同佢up乜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/f9BNQCwhzNZOLtKm7C/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h